		<lb n="10" break="no"/>m āka
	</p>

	<p>
		Iv-Aṟupatiṉ kaḻañcu poṉṉuṅ <unclear>koṇ</unclear>ṭu <gap reason="undefined" quantity="2" unit="character"/>
		<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>m</unclear> puḻaṟ-kōṭṭattu nā<unclear>yaṟu</unclear>nāṭṭu-p <unclear>pūtūrilum</unclear> <gap reason="undefined" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
