		<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṉ-vāy m<choice><orig>u</orig><reg>ū</reg></choice>ṉṟu mañcāṭi-p poṉ palicai-Āka Ā
		<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṇṭu-varai Oṉpatiṉ kaḻañcu poṉṉ-Āka <unclear>Ivv-ā</unclear>
		<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṭṭai tiru-mutal-āka Aṟ-āṟu tiṅkaṇāḷāl nāṟ-ka
		<lb n="16" break="no"/>ḻañc’ arai po<choice><sic>n</sic><corr>ṉ</corr></choice>ṉum tiru-v-oṟṟiyūr āṇi-k kiḻai
